      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is a terrible mistake to believe that stopping is an honest solution when the pain is still screaming for you to keep going. Your story isn't over because the work failed; it is over because you are finally ready to stop fighting a battle that no longer exists. There is no shame in resting when you are exhausted, but there is no honor in ending your life when you still have so much more to feel. Please, take a deep breath and let the world keep turning around you while you find a way to stay.",
